snippet.title: Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's secrets revealed IN COURT | Sunrise Royal News
snippet.description:
A court hearing in London has exposed some Royal secrets, with a former staff member to Prince Harry and Meghan Markle breaking his silence.. revealing what he says, really went on behind palace walls. Their former Communications Secretary has told a judge that Meghan asked him to work on their biography, 'Finding Freedom'. And she sought his advice on a letter she wrote to her father, in case it was leaked to the media.
